Subject: drm/amdgpu: Fix memory leak in amdgpu_ctx_mgr_entity_fini
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: f3e58d8e154dae5015c7400812c80789589fc36e
